{"tid":1833512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年初二「禁止公眾集會」，大家千祈唔好宣傳、召集及參與！","createTime":"2020-01-22T02:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T03:32:39.000Z","uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2cfcf510123b3b9dd3ae82182c341ac228515ffd","tid":1833512,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"香港本土起義成員接獲警方決定，對於該成員在1月26日（年初二）晚上計劃於旺角舉辦的「勿忘魚蛋、捍衛本土紀念集會」的申請，發出「禁止公眾集會通知」，禁止任何宣傳、召集及參與有關集會，屬罕有做法。由於上訴申請需時，香港本義會考慮是否提出上訴，並在未來舉行記者會交待詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100570071439694/posts/126927432137291/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100570071439694%2Fposts%2F126927432137291%2F&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=ff422062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100570071439694/posts/126927432137291/</a>"},{"pid":"b1c90509300a2b023bb2f232c49d17dc5e293e0f","tid":1833512,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89de416829944dab448c1f036d50dd8765701cc6","tid":1833512,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"咁「宣傳集會被反對，禁止」都得掛， 唔講，鬼知唔俾啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5198c94153949ced2d899edabd78d602dbb4e9","tid":1833512,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"果日本來同親戚去mk酒樓食飯<br />\n睇黎都唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda0f09f2bbf7c6bdf1f7a9241c4bc0929844a4e","tid":1833512,"uid":189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd5198c94153949ced2d899edabd78d602dbb4e9","tid":1833512,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"果日本來同親戚去mk酒樓食飯<br />\n睇黎都唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" clas